title: GDG DevFest West 2015 Summary
brief: GDG DevFest West 2015 is now over. It was a great success. We are happy to share with you some facts, emotions and, of course, photos from the biggest Google Developers Conference in West Cameroon!

title: Google IO 2016 Summary
brief: Google IO 2016 is now over. It was a great success. We are happy to share with you some facts, emotions and, of course, photos from the biggest Google Developers Event in Dschang Cameroon!

title: GDG DevFest 2016 Announced
brief: Cameroon West Google Developers Groups are proud to announce the fifth annual GDG DevFest 2016 which is the biggest Google related event in Dschang carefully crafted by GDG community! The event will take place on **26th of November**.

title: Call for Papers Time
brief: GDG DevFest 2016 announced! The 5th edition of the biggest conference about Google technologies in west cameroon will take on **November 26** in a city of Dschang. That means that it is time to open [call for talk submissions](https://plus.google.com/events/cjchmpkpooi2mico16mh5ora03k).
